},{"pid":"5c715de32d67fcd00896f79912f5d8f80e1ebe8b","tid":541720,"uid":50253,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T02:06:13.000Z","msg":"引力互吸兩者咪痴埋一齊<br />\n唔明樓主想問咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e0fefc3bafa72db677cc2d2f120b309dd5a229a","tid":541720,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T03:36:33.000Z","msg":"力有4重 <br />\n電磁力<br />\n重力（你講既引力）<br />\n強力 （原子偏核吸引力係其中一種）<br />\n弱力<br />\n<br />\n所以無左你講既引力，唔會使物質「分解」，無左 強力同弱力 先會。<br />\n<br />\n外國有套野好好睇， 叫優雅的字宙， 同一個系列有講 量子力學（4力），你睇晒會明多好多。 <br />\nYouTube 全齊"},{"pid":"ee091251e4c75ce7fdeddb1ad3ac6d98bd42e754","tid":541720,"uid":3581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T06:11:25.000Z","msg":"其實剩係intermolecular force 都分為<br />\n<br />\nIon-induced dipole forces<br />\ndipole-dipole interaction<br />\nHydrogen bonding<br />\nvan der Waals forces （dispersion forces)<br />\n<br />\n如果你剩係講無左萬有引力<br />\n<br />\nmolecules 係唔會粉碎"},{"pid":"c462b260ebfdb33b12874ce1de23965eb0a89605","tid":541720,"uid":10133,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b738706b2edbf2ad7d5662306eba1e069683a222","tid":541720,"uid":3179,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T23:09:15.000Z","msg":"睇完科普書就上黎想扮學者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T06:45:03.000Z","msg":"學術台係要討論架啦，下下孤芳自賞以為自己世界第一咩"},{"pid":"ca7a8662ff3d7a947ac7afc6462a912ed0e77b8d","tid":541720,"uid":123956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e0fefc3bafa72db677cc2d2f120b309dd5a229a","tid":541720,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T03:36:33.000Z","msg":"力有4重 <br />\n電磁力<br />\n重力（你講既引力）<br />\n強力 （原子偏核吸引力係其中一種）<br />\n弱力<br />\n<br />\n所以無左你講既引力，唔會使物質「分解」，無左 強力同弱力 先會。<br />\n<br />\n外國有套野好好睇， 叫優雅的字宙， 同一個系列有講 量子力學（4力），你睇晒會明多好多。 <br />\nYouTube 全齊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T07:44:22.000Z","msg":"大感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6e27b6b53f48dbcb37345d44069c9333ca0f257","tid":541720,"uid":38528,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T08:55:11.000Z","msg":"我覺得樓主問得幾好喎屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n讀過量子力學,知道晒世界有咩力,都要諗一諗先答到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪一味屌啦,香港就係成日有班人扮撚晒野咁,&quot;自己上網搵啦&quot;, &quot;無知&quot;,搞到冇人問野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇下依家教育就知D學生比人當鴨咁塞,唔明又唔問,問完驚比人笑,支持樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}